{{!< default}}

{{!-- "Radio" custom template — every Midnight Radio post in Ghost is
     assigned to this. Renders the same partial as post.hbs dispatches
     to when primary_tag is "midnight-radio", so the two routes stay
     identical. Keeping this file around (instead of unassigning the
     template in admin across 42 posts) means new MR posts pick up the
     reader automatically if the writer remembers to assign Radio —
     and even if they don't, the post.hbs primary_tag dispatch catches
     it as long as the midnight-radio tag is primary. --}}

{{#post}}
  {{> "midnight-radio/_episode"}}
{{/post}}
